Questions maid service owners usually ask us…
---------------------------------------------

Is the trial really free?

Yes, when you sign up today you’ll have 14 days free access to the best software on the market for maid services. No hidden fees or surprise bills.

How can I upgrade my plan?

You can upgrade your plan directly from the [settings of your account](https://app.zenmaid.com/settings/new-billing). After upgrading your plan, you will immediately gain access to all the features included in it. No need to reach out to Zenmaid’s team. If you have any further questions, we’re here and happy to help!

Can I cancel anytime?

Yes, you can cancel anytime your free trial and your subscription directly from the settings of your account.

What happens when I reach the limit of the Zenmaid's Starter Plan?

With Zenmaid's Starter Plan, you’re limited to 40 appointments per month. When you reach this limit, you will not be able to add other appointments to your team for the existing month. You will be shown a message that redirects you directly to the billing settings, where you will be able to upgrade to Zenmaid Pro Plan or Zenmaid Pro Max Plan.

I don't have time to enter all my clients ... Can ZenMaid help?

You bet we can! Just send us over your current client information however you have it and the ZenMaid team will format and upload it to your new account. FREE!

What happens to my client information? Do I still own it?

Yes, ZenMaid’s terms of service state that the only right we have to your clients’ information is to assist you with your account. You own any and all data you keep in ZenMaid.

Is there a contract or long-term commitment?

No, you can try any of ZenMaid’s plans on a month-to-month agreement, no signature necessary. If ZenMaid isn’t for you you can cancel anytime.

Is ZenMaid Secure?

Yes, your payment information and customer information is safe with us.

Discover just how affordable ZenMaid is for your maid service. See all the features and understand your pricing here.
